data.description: Low-maintenance desert landscaping graces the front yard of this handsome 2-story home across from a nice park in east El Paso. Tile flooring extends through a living area that boasts a stone-faced corner fireplace with gas logs where your family will love to gather on cool evenings. Steps away is the dining space featuring a granite-topped breakfast bar opening to the kitchen. Here you'll find an undermount sink & stainless steel appliances including a gas range with a microwave above. Loads of dark cabinets are complemented by tile backsplashes while the pantry gives even more storage. A laundry room with shelving & a half bath are also on the main floor. A carpeted loft leads to the sleeping quarters upstairs. There are 4 bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms. The main suite offers a twin-sink vanity, walk-in closet, & beautiful tile work. A covered patio in back opens to a good-sized backyard surrounded by privacy rock walls. A lovely family home, just waiting for you to move right in. Take a look today!
